{
  "stem": "21527.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we were-- there were probably about 100 in every carriage.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You couldn't move.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You couldn't stand up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You couldn't sit.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "You had no toilet facilities.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We were hungry.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We were thirsty.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "As I said before, it was very hot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "On the way, we stopped at various stations.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we-- and people-- and the Polish, the Polish population of that area all came to the trains just to see how the Jews were being transported.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And people were throwing jewelry to the Poles, begging them for a, for a sip of water.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And they just laughed and didn't give us any water.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "At one stage, the whole train stopped outside a huge gate.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And on top of the gate, there were huge doors.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And on top of the, the doors was a sign called Treblinka [NON-ENGLISH], which means Treblinka Jewish labor camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But of course, Treblinka was not a labor camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It was an extermination camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But to the outside world, the Germans presented themselves as benefactors of the Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And they let them be taken from the ghetto into places where they could work.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "It was just another lie that they used on the population.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "We stopped there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And we-- rumors had already started about Treblinka while we were still in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And the people were screaming and shouting.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Because we were all worried that we would be the ones which carriages would stop in Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "But by some-- I mean, there were lots and lots of miracles in our lives.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "That, that's all I can say.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Just fate said that we were to go on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And our train moved on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And we-- eventually, after stopping in a few places, we were taken to a camp called Blizyn, which is near Radom in Poland.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
